Since `company_id` is never returned in the `/api/auth/me` response, `user.company_id` is always `undefined`, which is falsy, so the check `!user.company_id` is ALWAYS true, causing the redirect!

This is the bug! The fix is either:
1. Add `company_id` to the `/api/auth/me` response
2. OR change the recruiter pages to check `role === 'recruiter'` instead of `company_id`

